# Code Architecture Rules

Full rules → `docs/governance/30-architecture-and-code-rules.md`
Design/UI patterns → `DESIGN_SYSTEM.md`
Image pipeline → `docs/IMAGE-PIPELINE.md`

## Critical reminders

- **Default: Server Component.** `"use client"` only for hooks/events/browser APIs
- Never `"use client"` at page level (exception: `/contact/page.tsx` — do not refactor)
- `below-fold`: wrap each section individually — never one large wrapper around all sections
- `dynamic()` for QuoteModal, StickyCTABar, ReviewsSection — do NOT also wrap in `below-fold`
- Always `<ResponsiveImage>` — never Next.js `<Image>`
- Never import `buildSrcSet`/`getFallbackSrc`/`image-manifest.json` in `"use client"` — manifest leak
- Design tokens only (`bg-primary`, `text-foreground`) — no hex in `className` (hero gradient `style={}` is OK)
- Tailwind v4: `bg-linear-to-r` not `bg-gradient-to-r`
